findings.title: Owner can change the token buying rate
findings.description: The owner has the privilege to modify the token buying rate.

findings.title: Owner can change the minimum buy amount
findings.description: The contract owner has the privilege to modify the minimum buy amount.

findings.title: Owner can start and finish sales any time
findings.description: The owner has privileges to start and finish sales at any time without restrictions.

findings.title: Owner Privileges: Whitelist Management
findings.description: The owner has the capability to enable whitelist and add/remove users to whitelist, which can lead to potential security risks if not properly managed.

findings.title: Owner can pause transfer any time
findings.description: The contract owner has the privilege to pause token transfers at any time without restrictions.
